description: Develop an interactive responsive website using HTML, CSS,JavaScript and its modern Frameworks.
question: What you need to know before you get started with UI Engineer?
answer: UI Engineer is also known as User Interface Engineer whose job is to think from the user perspective and to design websites and web applications that are attractive and extremely functional.

title: Backend Developer
description: Build beautiful websites with CMS features using Python and Django web framework.
question: What you need to know before you get started with Backend Developer?
answer: Back-end developers are web developers who concentrate on the data that is stored or accessed on a website or through an app. Their role is to develop systems and programs that ensure that the right data is accessed through the proper means.

title: DevOps Engineer
description: Build, publish and maintain web application.
question: What you need to know before you get started with DevOps Engineer?
answer: DevOps is a set of methods that combines software development and IT operations. It aims to reduce the friction between the systems development life-cycle and provide continuous delivery with high software quality.

title: Web Application Developer
description: Build an entire Web application with Frontend, Backend and API connections.
question: What you need to know before you get started with Web Application Developer?
answer: A web application developer is responsible for maintaining and building software applications according to the clients specifications and also evaluating codes to ensure industry standards.

title: Mobile Application Developer
description: Creating iOS and Android Applications and publishing on respective platform
question: What you need to know before you get started with Mobile Application Developer?
answer: Mobile application developers should be able to produce applications for Android and iOS in accordance with UI and UX trends which are functional as well as elegant.
